---
title: Sweet Potato and Spinach Pilaf with Parmesan and Chili
description: This sweet and savoury pilaf is packed with nutritious brown rice, baby spinach and pumpkin seeds (also called 'pepitas!') Pepitas are high in fibre magnesium and zinc, which helps your body to maintain a healthy immune system.
